OL,3,CFarmer proposes by mowing 'marry me'
OL,4,Cinto his field
OL,6,FA Somerset farmer has proposed to his
OL,7,Fgirlfriend by mowing "marry me" into
OL,8,Fhis field.
OL,10,FChloe Morley was completely unaware of
OL,11,Fher boyfriend Tom Heal's plans as she
OL,12,Fbrought him his dinner while he was
OL,13,Fworking late on Friday 17 May.
OL,15,FBut Tom had cut the question in huge
OL,16,Fletters into grass in his field near
OL,17,FHinkley Point, for Chloe to see as the
OL,18,Fsun set.
OL,20,F"It was a massive surprise", Chloe
OL,21,Ftold ITV News.
