OL,3,CFarmer proposes by mowing 'marry me'
OL,4,Cinto his field
OL,6,F"I had no idea at all until I got to
OL,7,Fthe field, and even then, I was deep
OL,8,Fin conversation and didn't see it
OL,9,Fstraight away."
OL,11,F'I was shaking and completely
OL,12,Foverwhelmed with emotions'
OL,14,FThe couple met through youth
OL,15,Forganisation Young Farmers and have
OL,16,Fbeen together four years.
OL,18,FChloe, who is 27, works as a
OL,19,Fveterinary nurse in Highbridge while
OL,20,FTom is a farmer from Bridgwater.
