OL,3,CFarmer proposes by mowing 'marry me'
OL,4,Cinto his field
OL,6,FChloe explained that it was a normal
OL,7,FFriday evening when Tom asked her to
OL,8,Fbring him his dinner, which "isn't
OL,9,Funusual when it's silaging season".
OL,11,F"I was just chatting away to him about
OL,12,Fmy day and then he parked up on the
OL,13,Fedge of the field and said we needed
OL,14,Fto get out," she said.
OL,16,F"I clocked the field and could just
OL,17,Fabout see what it said and I just
OL,18,Fmelted!
OL,20,F"I was shaking so much and completely
OL,21,Foverwhelmed with emotions."
