OL,3,CFarmer proposes by mowing 'marry me'
OL,4,Cinto his field
OL,6,FChloe says she said 'yes' as soon as
OL,7,Fshe managed to get the words out and
OL,8,Fthe couple are now happily engaged.
OL,10,FExplaining how he came up with the
OL,11,Fidea, Chloe added that it took Tom
OL,12,Fabout an hour to create the message in
OL,13,Fthe grass.
OL,15,F"But he did have help from GPS in the
OL,16,Ftractor to get his lines straight,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,19,FWhile the happy couple are hoping to
OL,20,Fget married soon, the demands of the
OL,21,Ffarm are taking priority.
