OL,3,CFarmer proposes by mowing 'marry me'
OL,4,Cinto his field
OL,6,F"We're hoping to marry next
OL,7,FSeptember", Chloe said.
OL,9,F"But currently it's life as normal and
OL,10,Fcontinuing with silaging!"
OL,12,FThe pair posted about their engagement
OL,13,Fon Facebook and have now received
OL,14,Fhundreds of comments from friends,
OL,15,Ffamily and beyond.
OL,17,F"We are truly overwhelmed with the
OL,18,Fresponse that the proposal has
OL,19,Fgotten", Chloe said.
